Guideline text:

FinEdge Capital – Brand Guidelines (Summary)

Logo:
- Use only the official full-color logo on white or light grey backgrounds.
- Minimum logo width: 40 mm (preferred 50 mm).
- Do not use white logo except on dark blue background.
- Logo must always appear in top right corner.
- Do not rotate, recolor, or add effects.
- Maintain clear spacing equal to height of the “F” in FinEdge.

Colors:
Primary:
- Deep Blue: #0A1F44
Secondary:
- Steel Grey: #6B7280
- Light Grey: #E5E7EB
Accent:
- Gold: #C8A96A

Color usage:
- Presentations must use blue and grey as base.
- Gold is only used for highlights or key metrics.
- Avoid overly colorful slides.

Typography:
- Brand font: Times New Roman (external)
- Office font: Arial
- Always use Arial for PowerPoint.

Style:
- Minimal, formal, structured.
- Avoid playful elements.
- Prefer left-aligned titles and content.